<i>♪ When they're drunk ♪</i>

17
00:01:06,733 --> 00:01:11,863
<i>♪ They don't play cards quite right ♪</i>

18
00:01:11,946 --> 00:01:14,906
<i>-♪ Tonight, tonight ♪</i>
-(bottle shatters)

19
00:01:14,991 --> 00:01:18,161
<i>♪ I won't get drunk tonight ♪</i>

20
00:01:18,244 --> 00:01:21,504
<i>♪ Without a beer, my head will clear ♪</i>

21
