<i>♪ Tonight ♪</i>

22
00:01:25,126 --> 00:01:27,836
{\an8}<i>♪ It's fun to trick a rummy ♪</i>

23
00:01:27,921 --> 00:01:31,341
{\an8}<i>♪ To put liquor in his tummy ♪</i>

24
00:01:31,424 --> 00:01:34,434
<i>♪ Your friendship's a delight ♪</i>

25
